name: Jeanne Boulet
bio:
I'm fond of video games since my childhood so I directed my studies to work in this field.

After graduating from high school, I did a 2-year course in a science preparatory class to prepare for the engineering schools entrance exams. I'm currently in 3nd year of computer science engineering studies at ESIEE Paris.

I'm a passionate about fitness which I have been doing in the gym for 2 years
